    • Method Detail

      • getData

        ByteBuffer getData()
        Returns:
        a byte buffer containing a message pay-load data. Logically, this buffer belongs to application at the point this object is supplied to the DeliveryListener. That is to say that once passed to the DeliveryListener the client will never modify the data held in this buffer.
